<section class="reviews mod book-content">
    <header>
        <a href="new_review" rel="nofollow" class="create-review redbutt rr" 
            data-isverify="False"
            data-verify-url="https://www.douban.com/accounts/phone/verify?redir=https://book.douban.com/subject/25928734/new_review">
            <span>我要写书评</span>
        </a>
        <h2>
            古典风格的书评 · · · · · ·
            <span class="pl">(<a href="reviews">全部 5 条</a>)</span>
        </h2>
    </header>


        


<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="7125020">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7125020/" class="title-link">翻译给85分吧</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7125020"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/2361004/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2361004/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">余超</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2014-10-11"
      class="main-meta">2014-10-11 12:09:18</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7125020_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  Rosen论三位作曲家器乐作品的文字，外人没法插嘴。放眼天下音乐学家，死的活的都算上，Rosen也就是对Donald F. Tovey一人比较服气而已。Rosen记性好，耳朵好，又敢说。莫扎特的钢琴协奏曲，几张唱片，几本谱子，够啃一辈子的，跟Rosen学习怎么啃，学会了就是一辈子受用了。  不...

